{"tid":1401453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線思維洗腦：Be smart. Be water. 醒水，散水","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T10:40:36.000Z","uid":17502,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4afe419024fcfbfe2e5285d79b60dc0684f49966","tid":1401453,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撤退不等於失敗</span><br />\n<br />\n目的唔係增加清場困難，而係<br />\n<br />\n迅速出現，迅速干擾，迅速消失<br />\n<br />\n務求令對方一頭霧水<br />\n<br />\n見唔到人，搵唔到人，捉唔到人<br />\n<br />\n要承認正面衝突一定唔夠打<br />\n<br />\n迅速撤退，無影無蹤先係醒目仔<br />\n<br />\n所以前線嘅黃金定律係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Be smart, be water<br />\n<br />\n醒水，散水</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追。」"},{"pid":"395e04ec4cc246bd715ea920c3f2201beaed99a4","tid":1401453,"uid":108337,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:48:07.000Z","msg":"85一齊幫人被罷工仲好啦<br />\n今日做晒任務仲戀戰都唔知有乜意義"},{"pid":"e0617d93db9833f1d10e06c3be1da0bc712df9cd","tid":1401453,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:48:27.000Z","msg":"Be smart, be water<br />\n<br />\n醒水，散水"},{"pid":"8217199dcb0fdee23307ece4ed0b66342c9692f1","tid":1401453,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4afe419024fcfbfe2e5285d79b60dc0684f49966","tid":1401453,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">撤退不等於失敗</span><br />\n<br />\n目的唔係增加清場困難，而係<br />\n<br />\n迅速出現，迅速干擾，迅速消失<br />\n<br />\n務求令對方一頭霧水<br />\n<br />\n見唔到人，搵唔到人，捉唔到人<br />\n<br />\n要承認正面衝突一定唔夠打<br />\n<br />\n迅速撤退，無影無蹤先係醒目仔<br />\n<br />\n所以前線嘅黃金定律係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Be smart, be water<br />\n<br />\n醒水，散水</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"一三五罷買!!<br />\n<br />\n85之後<br />\n<br />\n[參考波蘭成功例子既最佳戰術] 完全剋制政府冷處理 - 罷買 <br />\n一個最有效既長期戰術, 麻煩入去睇睇<br />\n<br />\n1. 週期性罷買係相當可行既一個戰術, 因為更能夠令普通人適應<br />\n2. 罷買影響力可以好大<br />\n3. 政府用冷處理戰術,打算拖至9月,而罷買係開學之後一樣可以實行,可以向社會施加壓力既最好方法<br />\n4. 罷買比遊行, 三罷, 更能夠說服中立派/和理非行動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1397444/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1397444/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"928117339319eb77c44a766cab530baaecfa3b75","tid":1401453,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:48:59.000Z","msg":"Be smart, be water<br />\n<br />\n醒水，散水"},{"pid":"d28cde4b2b4f8fda915fc34b8343bc539df3b395","tid":1401453,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:49:25.000Z","msg":"Be smart, be water<br />\n<br />\n醒水，散水"},{"pid":"07556df7d6ee36c520de54fee4849546a1394763","tid":1401453,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:49:58.000Z","msg":"Be smart, be water<br />\n<br />\n醒水，散水"},{"pid":"199b761a1ddd82fbf47586d5e142a2809b4f75f4","tid":1401453,"uid":209282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c002144540e96e6748799c5b4f26db9e8042b6","tid":1401453,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"Be smart, be water<br />\n<br />\n醒水，散水"},{"pid":"8211c6f6d24979d0edbb92df716c0d5a8b180329","tid":1401453,"uid":80259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:50:57.000Z","msg":"點解每次都有人要留到被人拉<br />\n俾你撐到1點，2點，咁又點？<br />\n得到d咩？<br />\n第2日齊齊再出黎好過啦<br />\n燒野又係無謂，反而令更多人反感"},{"pid":"e97b99f53c9224d4933ecb4c4197f7fd94d8858f","tid":1401453,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:51:13.000Z","msg":"Be smart, be water<br />\n<br />\n醒水，散水"},{"pid":"d841f634793409f898ca6d107ad688fd084a17c1","tid":1401453,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:51:58.0